channel.title: Deltascape v16 original source?
channel.description: I'm not sure if this is the right section, but does anyone have the original Deltascape v16 Source and client? Where you log in at Falador gardens? Every "Deltascape" source I download is clearly a Czar base where they removed everything and changed the home to Lumbridge. Combat doesn't even work properly on these sources. I would really like to find the original Delta!
